			    </h1>
				<p class="P28"><span class="T3">
<p class="c5"><span class="c3 c1">THE MIDDLE - The Gotta Gotta Getaway Sweepstakes</span></p><p class="c5"><span class="c3 c1">OFFICIAL RULES </span></p><p class="c8 c9"><span class="c1">&nbsp;</span><span class="c1 c3">NO PURCHASE NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN A PRIZE. &nbsp;A PURCHASE WILL NOT INCREASE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING. &nbsp;ODDS OF WINNING A PRIZE ARE DEPENDENT UPON THE NUMBER OF ELIGIBLE ENTRIES RECEIVED. &nbsp;VOID WHERE PROHIBITED.&nbsp; </span><span class="c1">The entry period for the &ldquo;Gotta Gotta Getaway&rdquo; Sweepstakes (&ldquo;Sweepstakes&rdquo;), sponsored by Warner Bros. Domestic Television Distribution ( &ldquo;Sponsor&rdquo;), begins Monday, October 21, 2013, at 12:00:01 a.m. Pacific Time (&ldquo;PT&rdquo;) and ends at 10:59:59 p.m. PT on Saturday, November 9, 2013 (the &ldquo;Sweepstakes Period&rdquo;). &nbsp;&nbsp;All federal, state and local laws and regulations apply.&nbsp; Proof of submitting a Sweepstakes entry will not be deemed by Sponsor as proof of receipt of entry into the Sweepstakes. &nbsp;Any attempted form of entry into the Sweepstakes other than as described herein is void.</span></p><p class="c9 c8"><span class="c3 c1">1. ELIGIBILITY:</span><span class="c1">&nbsp; </span></p><p class="c9 c8"><span class="c1">The Sweepstakes is open to individuals who meet the following criteria: &nbsp;(a) are eighteen (18) years of age or older, who (only applicable if using text method of entry) have a registered wireless account with Short Message Services (&ldquo;SMS&rdquo;) capability and/or wireless internet service, and (b) are a legal resident of and physically residing in one of the 50 United States or the District of Columbia (excluding Puerto Rico, Guam, American Samoa, United States territories, possessions, and protectorates, foreign based United States military installations and wherever restricted or prohibited by law) (&ldquo;Entrant&rdquo;). Neither Sponsor nor employees of Sponsor, &ldquo;The Middle&rdquo;, Time Warner, Warner Bros. Entertainment, Telepictures Productions Inc., Universal City Development Partners, Ltd. d/b/a Universal Orlando&reg; Resort (&ldquo;Prize Provider&rdquo;), and all of their respective partners, parent companies, divisions, subsidiaries, affiliates, trustees, advertising, promotion and public relations agencies, and their respective officers, directors, employees, agents, independent contractors, representatives and agencies (collectively, the &quot;Sweepstakes Entities&rdquo;) are eligible to participate in the Sweepstakes and/or win a Prize (as defined below).&nbsp; Additionally, immediate family members of such employees and persons living in the same household as such employees (whether related or not) are not eligible to win.&nbsp; For the purposes of this Sweepstakes, &ldquo;immediate family members&rdquo; is defined as spouse, domestic partner, mother, father, grandmother, grandfather, children, siblings and their spouses.&nbsp; </span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">By entering this Sweepstakes, Entrants agree to be bound by these Official Rules and the decisions of the Sponsor, which are final and binding in all respects and cannot be challenged or appealed.</span></p><p class="c2 c4"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c3 c1">HOW TO ENTER: </span><span class="c1">SMS and online entry is the only method of entry for the Sweepstakes. </span></p><p class="c2 c4"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Entries received before and/or after the Sweepstakes Period will be void. &nbsp;All entries become the sole property of Sponsor and will not be acknowledged or returned.</span></p><p class="c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c1">Sponsor&rsquo;s computer will serve as the official time piece for the Sweepstakes. </span></p><p class="c2"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c8"><span class="c3 c1 c7">To Enter</span><span class="c3 c1">:</span></p><p class="c2"><span class="c3 c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Participants can enter online at </span><span class="c10 c1 c7"><a class="c6" href="http://www.themiddleweekdays.com/sweepstakes/legal.php">http://www.themiddleweekdays.com/sweepstakes/legal.php</a></span><span class="c1">&nbsp;or by texting to 48307. &nbsp;Between October 21, 2013, and November 9, 2013, each syndicated episode of the television show &ldquo;The Middle&rdquo; (the &ldquo;Program&rdquo;) will feature a Family Member of the Day. To enter the Sweepstakes between October 21, 2013, and November 9, 2013, watch the Program (in participating broadcast markets only, check your local listings for the time and station), note the &ldquo;Family Member of the Day&rdquo; and submit th</span><span class="c1">e name of the &ldquo;</span><span class="c1">Family Member of the Day</span><span class="c1">&rdquo; either online by 11:59:59 pm (PT) on the day the word appeared during the Program or via text as instructed below. </span><span class="c1">All participants will be required to submit an entry into the Sweepstakes as outlined below</span><span class="c1">. </span><span class="c1">Entries that do not include the correct information in full or which are submitted other than outlined below will be disqualified.</span></p><p class="c2 c4"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">(i). </span><span class="c1 c7">Online Entry</span><span class="c1">: To enter online, visit </span><span class="c10 c1 c7"><a class="c6" href="http://www.themiddleweekdays.com/sweepstakes/legal.php">http://www.themiddleweekdays.com/sweepstakes/legal.php</a></span><span class="c1">&nbsp;and complete the Official Online Registration form by entering all of the required information and following all posted instructions. Depending on the date of your entry, you will be required to submit the applicable &ldquo;Family Member of the Day&rdquo; that appeared on the Program. &nbsp;If the Program did not feature a &ldquo;Family Member of the Day&rdquo; 